The paper involves using deep reinforcement learning to learn efficient heuristics for automated reasoning algorithms for quantified Boolean formulas. This falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with optimization and decision making (cs.DM), programming languages (cs.PL), and software engineering (cs.SE) as it focuses on improving the efficiency of a backtracking search algorithm.
